On March 9 from 12:00, a rehabilitation center for men affected by the celebration of March 8th will be open. The center is located at the address: garage cooperative "Highway", block No. 5.
We provide comfortable conditions for staying in the center and a full package of services: advice from Petrovich, a psychologist with 40 years of experience, comfortable pallets, a barbecue, a week's supply of meat, beer, smoked fish and sausages, educational board games and a GAZ-21 constructor.
